query:
SELECT 
  pq.id AS assignment_id,
  pq.accessCode,
  tq.questionnaireId,
  q.title AS questionnaire_title,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM questions WHERE questionnaireId = tq.questionnaireId) AS question_count
FROM partnerQuestionnaires pq
JOIN touchpointQuestionnaires tq ON pq.touchpointQuestionnaireId = tq.id
JOIN questionnaires q ON tq.questionnaireId = q.id
WHERE pq.accessCode = 'DDSETM9RNAHB';
